{"tid":2323442,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"甸恩軒達臣同蘇B攤牌：冇正選即走人","createTime":"2020-12-13T07:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T11:54:27.000Z","uid":147522,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"eabde1915d1d506124e18ce744ba75f9a56d23e3","tid":2323442,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"曼聯喺歐聯出局之後，球隊士氣大受打擊，更爆出兵變傳聞，根據英國《曼徹斯特晚報》爆料，曼聯2號門將甸恩軒達臣同領隊蘇斯克查攤牌，如果未能取代迪基亞，獲得正選位置，就會喺下月轉會市場重開後，要求離隊。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，呢位23歲英格蘭門將近日同蘇斯克查進行會談，重申自己已經做好準備，擔任正選，希望有更多上陣時間。事實上，甸恩軒達臣上季被外借去鍚菲聯期間，踢咗36場英超，表現備受肯定，但重返曼聯後，只能屈居後備。<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係正選門將嘅迪基亞表現欠佳，令甸恩軒達臣更加唔忿氣。蘇斯克查曾經透露上月對西布朗、巴沙克舒希，會畀甸恩軒達臣擔正，但結果冇兌現承諾，令甸恩軒達臣失去耐性，決定同蘇斯克查攤牌。"},{"pid":"ccdb14578ec527dba17187c536eb19e13a205075","tid":2323442,"uid":36238,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:53:16.000Z","msg":"Come liverpool la diu"},{"pid":"2d26395a06ff6fca4cb9a9e11090ddce7ae187a8","tid":2323442,"uid":2153,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccdb14578ec527dba17187c536eb19e13a205075","tid":2323442,"uid":36238,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:53:16.000Z","msg":"Come liverpool la diu"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:54:01.000Z","msg":"去利有正選?"},{"pid":"a8723fa81992526980ce655ad6f164a6d1f2b26e","tid":2323442,"uid":351028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d26395a06ff6fca4cb9a9e11090ddce7ae187a8","tid":2323442,"uid":2153,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccdb14578ec527dba17187c536eb19e13a205075","tid":2323442,"uid":36238,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:53:16.000Z","msg":"Come liverpool la diu"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:54:01.000Z","msg":"去利有正選?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:54:39.000Z","msg":"可能唔係猁迷<br />\n猁迷會賣Alisson??<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120b9a9f3864f03859